    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064280/extras/6c39bbc465206ca485b157a5eff27e18.avif?t=1772091330\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >屏幕那头，是主播惊恐无助的脸；屏幕这头，是她命运的唯一掌控者——你。一条突如其来的恐吓勒索信息，让这个直播夜晚瞬间坠入深渊。本作是一款全程采用真人演出的沉浸式互动电影游戏，你将亲身体验从天堂跌入地狱的惊魂时刻，感受令人窒息的悬疑氛围与情感冲击。主播的直播生涯甚至人生是否会就此终结？这一切，都始于你此刻的抉择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064280/extras/2f228adb5c28fe1cfa7c51472bf416d8.poster.avif?t=1772091330\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064280/extras/2f228adb5c28fe1cfa7c51472bf416d8.webm?t=1772091330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064280/extras/d1d3fb3dd03be2759457736d5a89e051.avif?t=1772091330\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你并非旁观者，而是局中人。在这里，你的每一个动作都至关重要：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >实时决策：在超过50个关键决策点中，你的选择将直接左右剧情走向，与角色共情，体验抉择时的紧张与纠结。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深度互动：仔细搜查场景中的每一个角落，与物品互动寻找蛛丝马迹；在突如其来的“快速反应事件”中果断操作，体验心跳加速的感觉。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回溯关键记忆：在关键时刻回溯至她的过去，逐渐揭开她与身边所有人之间错综复杂的关系，挖掘隐藏在情感背后的真相碎片。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064280/extras/1c5d7956624e677c64bdc007b3c3a0c3.poster.avif?t=1772091330\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064280/extras/1c5d7956624e677c64bdc007b3c3a0c3.webm?t=1772091330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064280/extras/1db42222a9e57bc79d260159d4abfd9b.avif?t=1772091330\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个没有标准答案的迷局中，你将完全主宰故事的终章。你的调查、你的判断、你与他人的每一次对话互动，都将共同汇向5个截然不同的结局。是找出真凶完美破局，还是陷入更深的阴谋？主播的命运是悲是喜，完全由你书写。请做好准备，承担你所有选择带来的后果，揭开黑幕后的真相，体验独一无二、充满代入感的惊心动魄之旅！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064280/extras/edcf29f100d12e8f73b2c597215b5401.poster.avif?t=1772091330\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064280/extras/edcf29f100d12e8f73b2c597215b5401.webm?t=1772091330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
